Summary: Something transparent with lights in the sky
divs: Sighting DetailsMid afternoon, well into the Mohave during the early afternoon of 2-9-2012. About two hours drive out of Trona, CA. I felt a sudden sense of urgency to stop the car. I got out and walked around for a few minutes, looking around but noticed nothing. I started snapping photos of the surrounding area. Did not notice anything unusual with the photos until today when I started reviewing them on my computer. It appears I captured lights and perhaps a shadow of something larger and smaller lights around the periphery. Larger object appears to be transparent. If a reflection, not sure of what, since there was nothing around me, no other vehicles and not a cloud in the sky. One of the lights appears to be emitting, as you can clearly see the edges. I saw nothing and heard nothing at the time. I saw no air craft and was looking for China Lake jet patrols but saw none. I have one photo saved on the original memory card at the time the photo was taken. I have attached it here. I wish I had more information to offer, but as earlier stated, I did not see anything that day, so perhaps this is nothing, but maybe...it could be something....
